i5.las2peer.services.calendar

Class Entry

  • java.lang.Object
    • i5.las2peer.services.calendar.Entry

  • public class Entry
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that represents a date created by the user. It will be used by the MyCalendar to organize dates.
    The class contains the start and of a date. Furthermore it contains the id of the creator.
